const reducerInitialObj = {
  expenseData: EXPENSE_DATA,
};

function reducer(state, action) {
  switch (action.type) {
    case "DELETE": {
      const newState = state.expenseData.filter(
        (element) => element.id !== action.id
      );

      return { ...state, expenseData: newState };
    }

    default:
      return state;
  }
}

function ExpenseDataProvider(props) {
  const [expenseDataState, expenseDataDispatch] = useReducer(
    reducer,
    reducerInitialObj
  );

  function removeExpenseData(id) {
    expenseDataDispatch({ type: "DELETE", id });
  }

  const contextInitialObj = {
    expenseData: expenseDataState.expenseData,
    removeExpenseData,
  };

  return (
    <ExpenseDataContext.Provider value={contextInitialObj}>
      {props.children}
    </ExpenseDataContext.Provider>
  );
}

export default ExpenseDataProvider;
